<h4 style="text-align:center;">Day 3: Break</h4>
<p>On the third day of our stay in Kothakota we did not have any programs planned, so we could do other things relating to the project. We assembled more bags and spoke to some local press about our project. I was extremely excited that the newspapers had taken an interest in my project and our team’s story, and this press also brought more attention to the project and allowed for even more people to decide to get vaccinated.</p><br>
<div class="row col-md-12">
