<h4 style="text-align:center;">Project Day 5: Sankireddipalli</h4>
<p>The 5th and final day of programming took place at Sankireddipalli. The MLA came to this event too and we were also joined by other local politicians who were highly respected by the people of the town. The programming was similar, but due to the amount of press, the introduction and speeches portion ran slightly longer to inform all the journalists about every aspect of the project. We also served lunch to the villagers who came to the program, and as usual gave those who got vaccinated goodie bags to thank them. At Sankireddipalli we were able to vaccinate close to 100 people. </p><br>
